short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find code from UI, or, find UI from code!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension works bidirectionally:
1. Click UI to find the source code. 
2. Click source code to find the UI.


To use, you must also install the vs-code extension below:

https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=n3rds-inc.visualwind
